dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Billy Wright. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Donna Green.
Nice to meet you, Donna. To assist you further, may I kindly ask for your date of birth in digits?
Sure, it's one nine seven five zero six zero three.
Thank you, Donna. And could you also provide the ZIP code of your residence for verification purposes, please?
Of course, it's zero eight six one zero.
Great! Thank you for providing that information, Donna. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all. Thank you for your help, Billy.
You're welcome, Donna. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance.
